And on another note rauq. In case you didnt know this was an idea worked out 
while BK was hostage. I agreed to let BK live and told Airly BK would have to 
return to the base however and the devices implemented would make sure of 
that. The possession type deal is something most infecticons can do to others 
but it is mostly to speak. The deal was set up, the devices were implanted, I 
told Airly when BK was either eliminated, won the entire IGL, or left it she 
would be made to return to the Infecticon base. She agreed, therefore the 
post would be legit as it was worked out.  Its too late to take back the 
entire thing just because now shes had a change of heart. She made the 
decision to have BK have those devices implanted, now she has to live with 
the consequences. Besides once again i state I told Proto(Crowlord, Hugar, 
etc) about it before doing it and he had no objections.

--part1_158.2c42650.29041ca2_boundary
